<view class="container">
  <view class="hero-card">
    <view class="hero-title">绑定老人</view>
    <view class="hero-desc">
      通过手机号、二维码或邀请链接找到老人账号，提交绑定申请后，由家庭管理员确认通过。
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="mode-tabs">
    <view class="mode-tab {{mode === 'phone' ? 'active' : ''}}" data-mode="phone" bindtap="setMode">手机号</view>
    <view class="mode-tab {{mode === 'scan' ? 'active' : ''}}" data-mode="scan" bindtap="setMode">扫码绑定</view>
    <view class="mode-tab {{mode === 'invite' ? 'active' : ''}}" data-mode="invite" bindtap="setMode">邀请链接</view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{mode === 'phone'}}" class="panel-card">
    <view class="panel-title">通过手机号查找老人</view>
    <view class="panel-desc">输入老人预留手机号，先查找账号，再发起绑定申请。</view>

    <input
      class="phone-input"
      type="number"
      maxlength="11"
      placeholder="请输入老人手机号"
      value="{{phone}}"
      bindinput="onPhoneInput"
    />

    <button class="primary-btn" bindtap="previewPhoneLookup">查找并申请绑定</button>

    <view class="flow-tip">
      <view class="tip-title">后续流程</view>
      <view class="tip-line">1. 找到对应老人账号</view>
      <view class="tip-line">2. 选择与老人的关系</view>
      <view class="tip-line">3. 由家庭管理员审核通过</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{mode === 'scan'}}" class="panel-card">
    <view class="panel-title">扫描二维码绑定</view>
    <view class="panel-desc">适合家属在老人身边时使用。扫描老人端展示的二维码即可发起申请。</view>

    <view class="scan-preview">
      <view class="scan-icon">▣</view>
      <view class="scan-text">扫描后将自动带出老人账号信息</view>
    </view>

    <button class="primary-btn" bindtap="previewScanFlow">扫描二维码</button>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{mode === 'invite'}}" class="panel-card">
    <view class="panel-title">通过邀请链接绑定</view>
    <view class="panel-desc">老人可在老人端点击“邀请家人”，通过微信将邀请发送给家属。</view>

    <view wx:if="{{loading}}" class="state-card">正在加载邀请信息...</view>

    <view wx:elif="{{sharedElder}}" class="invite-card">
      <view class="invite-badge">已收到邀请</view>
      <view class="invite-name">{{sharedElder.name}}</view>
      <view class="invite-meta">
        <text wx:if="{{sharedElder.gender}}">{{sharedElder.gender}}</text>
        <text wx:if="{{sharedElder.age}}">{{sharedElder.age}} 岁</text>
        <text wx:if="{{sharedElder.hometown}}">{{sharedElder.hometown}}</text>
      </view>
      <view wx:if="{{sharedElder.address}}" class="invite-address">{{sharedElder.address}}</view>

      <view wx:if="{{!requestSent}}" class="approval-box">
        <view class="approval-title">发送绑定申请</view>
        <view class="approval-desc">
          申请提交后，需要由家庭管理员确认通过，避免陌生人误绑定。
        </view>
        <button class="primary-btn" bindtap="submitInviteRequest">提交绑定申请</button>
      </view>

      <view wx:else class="state-card success">
        申请已提交，等待家庭管理员审批。审批通过后，你就能管理这位老人的回忆与健康信息。
      </view>
    </view>

    <view wx:elif="{{!loading}}" class="state-card">
      当前没有可用的邀请链接，请让老人端重新发起邀请。
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel-card pending-card">
    <view class="panel-title">待处理申请</view>
    <view class="panel-desc">这里会显示你已经提交、正在等待家庭管理员审批的绑定申请。</view>

    <view wx:for="{{pendingRequests}}" wx:key="id" class="pending-item">
      <view>
        <view class="pending-name">{{item.elderName}}</view>
        <view class="pending-meta">{{item.relation}} · {{item.statusText}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="pending-badge">审批中</view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
